data.enText: a person who works underwater, usually with special equipment
a person who jumps into the water with their head first and their arms in front of them

tr: large somewhat primitive fish-eating diving bird of the northern hemisphere having webbed feet placed far back

value.def: A diver is a person who swims under water using special breathing equipment.

example.ex: Police divers have recovered the body of a sixteen year old boy.
example.tran: 警方潜水员已经找到了一名16岁男孩的尸体。
